node.text: Who doesn’t love a Q&A? @Bumble came by to play the Question Game while I spent a few moments resting and recharging at home. Watch my episode now! #BumblePartner

node.text: I had a wonderful conversation with Bryan Stevenson, the founder and Executive Director of @eji_org. We've worked together before, and I can't wait to work with him in the future.

node.text: I was heartbroken to have to withdraw today after injuring my right leg. My love and gratitude are with the fans and the team who make being on centre court so meaningful. Feeling the extraordinary warmth and support of the crowd today when I walked on - and off - the court meant the world to me.

node.text:
One of my favorite necklaces now comes in 4 colors! It’s our new Unstoppable Brilliance collection by @serenawilliamsjewelry. Chic orange, goes-with-everything black, crisp white, and of course PINK. Each necklace has added sparkle with baguette diamonds, and the reverse is engraved with ‘Unstoppable’ to inspire you every day. Link in my bio for more.
⁠
Through 7/15/2021, we are donating a portion of proceeds from Unstoppable Brilliance to Accion Opportunity Fund's Small Business Relief Fund that provides support directly to Black small-business owners.
